'''Insider''' is an article written by [[Morrie Mullins (real person)|Morrie Mullins]] as a tie-in to the [[Living Force (roleplaying campaign)|Living Force]] campaign. It was published on the [[Wizards of the Coast]] website on [[May 26]], [[2005]] and took the form of a [[HoloNet/Legends|HoloNet]] poster warning that [[Cris Tosiren|Sot-sirc]] was back in the [[Cularin system/Legends|Cularin system]]. It was shortly after Sot-sirc was last in the system that [[Len Markus]] discovered the [[Darkstaff]] and the system [[Cularin's disappearance|vanished]] from the galaxy for 10 years.

The article was followed by roleplaying statistics for Sot-sirc.

